---
title: "School of Biological & Envrionmental Sciences"
---

Department within Liverpool John Moores University [BES](https://www.ljmu.ac.uk/about-us/faculties/faculty-of-science/school-of-biological-and-environmental-sciences)

## Diverse Research Interests

Within the school, we work on topics spanning from behavioural ecology to genomics and genetics, parasite-host interactions, neuro-endocrinology, forensic anthropology, marine biology, environmental physiology and dinosaur locomotion to wildlife conservation - all united by the use of R and R Studio.